  <span id="freeText3065768628140102738" style="display:none">The Duke of Jervaulx was brilliant - and dangerous. Considered dissolute, reckless, and extravagant, he was transparently referred to as the "D of J" in scandal sheets. But sometimes the most womanizing rakehell can be irresistible, and even his most causal attentions fascinated the sheltered Maddy Timms. <br /><br />Then one fateful day she receives the shocking news - the duke is lost to the world. And Maddy knows it is her destiny to help him and her only chance to find the true man behind the wicked facade. <br /><br />But she never dreamed her gentle, healing touch would alter his life and her own so completely - and bind them together in need, desire...and love.</span>
