<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/23890.Laura_Kinsale"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1260172742p3/23890.jpg);'></div>
